==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: euphoria
<hw>euphoria</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>a strong pleasant feeling of
well-being or happiness; it is often caused by attainment of a desired
goal or other incident of accomplishment, but may irrationally accompany
a pathological manic state.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> elation, high.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>euphoriant</ent>⟦br⟧
